<head>
<title>Effects of Marijuana</title>
</head>

<body>

<h1>Effects of Marijuana</h1>

<p>Marijuana can halt the progress of glaucoma and combat nausea
caused by chemotherapy or prescription drugs. Numerous medical
experts have endorsed its use, including the prestigious
<a href="/revolution/body/drugs/critics/jom.html">New England
Journal of Medicine</a>.</p>

<p>In addition to medical use, the hemp plant (marijuana) has many industrial
uses. Hemp is a more quickly renewable source of pulp for paper, and its
fibers have been used for centuries in rope, canvas and other uses. Prohibition,
in a vain attempt at eliminating recreational use, succeeds in eliminating
all these beneficial uses.</p>

<P>Hemp has a rich history. <a href="bales.html">Hemp bales</a> have even
been used as a military defense.</p>

