<head>
<title>Breckenridge Supports Medical Marijuana</title>
<!-- Place: Breckenridge, Colorado (USA) -->
<!-- Time: April 1994 -->
</head>

<body>

<h1>Breckenridge supports medical marijuana</h1>

<p>From a posting by <a href="/revolution/by_name/N/NORML.html">NORML</a>:</p>

<p>In April 1994, residents of <a
href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/co/Breckenridge.html">Breckenridge</a>,
<a href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/co/">Colorado</a> voted 261-213
in favor of an
ordinance ordering the police chief and district attorney to make the arrest
and prosecution of those using or cultivating marijuana for medical purposes
their lowest priority.</p>

