<head>
<title>Joseph MacNamara</title>
</head>

<body>

<h1>Joseph MacNamara</h1>

<p>Joseph MacNamara is a former police chief of San Jose, <a
href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/ca/">California</a>,
and is currently a research fellow with the
<a href="/revolution/by_name/H/Hoover.html">Hoover Institution</a>.
MacNamara is a leading advocate of repealing drug prohibition.</p>

<p>Appearances in <b>Revolution</b>:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/revolution/by_name/D/DPF.html">Drug Policy Foundation</a></li>
<li><a href="/revolution/body/drugs/critics/hoover.html">Hoover
	Resolution</a></li>
<li><a href="/revolution/body/drugs/legal/lying.html">Cops
	lie to make drug arrests</a></li>
</ul>

