<h1>Andre Marrou</h1>

<p>Andre Marrou was one of four Libertarians elected to the
<a href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/ak/">Alaska</a> state
House of Representatives. Marrou later was the 1992 presidential candidate
of the
<a href="/revolution/by_name/L/LPUS.html">Libertarian Party</a>.</p>

