<head>
<title>David Nolan</title>
</head>

<body>

<h1>David Nolan</h1>

<p>David Nolan was one of the founders the
<A href="/revolution/by_name/L/LPUS.html">Libertarian Party</a>. In fact
the Party was founded in his Westminster, Colorado living room in 1971.
Nolan is also the originator of the famous "Nolan Chart" popularized by the
<a href="/revolution/by_name/A/ASG.html">Advocates for Self-Government</a>
as the "World's Smallest Political Quiz."</p>

<p>Contact:</p>
<address>
email: <img src="/images/mail.gif" alt="[EMAIL]"><a
href="mailto:73303.1612@compuserve.com">73303.1612@compuserve.com</a><br>
</address>

<p>Appearances in <b>Revolution</b>:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/revolution/politics/lpus/lpco/lpday.html">
	Westminster proclaims Libertarian Party Day</a></li>
</ul>

</body>
