<html>

<head>
<title>Lawyer Jokes</title>
</head>

<body>

<h1>Lawyer Jokes</h1>

<hr>

<h2>Difference Between Catfish and Lawyers</h2>

<p>The difference between a catfish and a lawyer is that one is a
scumsucking bottom feeder, and the other is just a fish.</p>

<hr>

<h2>Lawyers and Lab Rats</h2>

<p>Scientists are considering using lawyers in place of rats in lab
experiments. Researchers get less attached to them and there are some
things rats just won't do.</p>

<hr>

<h2>That's Not Funny</h2>

<P>The problem with lawyer jokes is that lawyers don't think
they're funny, and no one else thinks they're jokes.</p>

