<head>
<title>War</title>
</head>

<body>

<h1>War</h1>

<ul>
<li>Wars and revolutions
	<ul>
	<li>1898-1904: <a href="phillipine.html">Phillipine-American
		War</a></li>
	<li>1933-1945: <a href="WWII/">World War II</a></li>
	<li>1947 - present: <a href="kashmir.html">India and Pakistan
		fight over Kashmir</a></li>
	<li>1949 - present: <a href="taiwan.html">Tensions between
		China and Taiwan</a></li>
	<li>1975 - present: <a href="etimor/">Indonesia's genocide
		of East Timor</a></li>
	<li>1983 - present: <a href="tamil.html">Sri Lankan civil war</a></li>
	<li>1989: <a href="tiananmen.html">Tian An Men</a>: China's near
		revolution</a></li>
	<li>1991-1995: <a href="somalia.html">Somalia's civil war</a></li>
	<li>1990's: <a href="bosnia/">Bosnia's ethnic conflict</a></li>
	<li>1995 - 1996: <a href="chechnya.html">Chechyna</a>:
		Russians attack breakaway republic</li>
	<li>1996: <a href="aegean.html">The Aegean Sea:</a> possible
		Greek-Turkish conflict</li>
	</ul>
<li>Terrorism
	<ul>
