<head>
<title>Immigration</title>
</head>

<body>

<h1>Immigration and Emigration</h1>

<p>Libertarians believe in free immigration and emigration. No one has
the right to decide where another person can live or work.</p>

<ul>
<li><a href="esmor.html">October 1995: prison camp guards torture
	immigrants</a></li>
</ul>

