<h2>Jefferson on Legalese</h2>

<p>That has happened which generally happens -- doubts have been produced
by the too great number of words used to prevent doubt.</p>

<p>-- <a href="/revolution/by_name/J/ThomasJefferson.html">Thomas
Jefferson</a>, concerning a treaty with France, submitted to Congress
January 18, 1791</p>

