<body>

<h1>Bombing of Pan Am Flight 103 Over Lockerbie</h1>

<p>In late 1988, Pan Am Flight 103 exploded over <a
href="/revolution/by_place/Europe/UK/Lockerbie.html">Lockerbie</a>, Scotland.
Investigators traced the source of the bomb to Arab terrorists.</p>

<ul>
