<head>
<title>Oklahoma City Bombing</title>
<!-- Place: Oklahoma City, Oklahoma (USA) -->
<!-- Time: bomb April 19, 1995 -->
</head>

<body>

<h1>Oklahoma City Bombing</h1>

<p>Shortly after 9 a.m. April 19, 1995, a bomb destroyed the Alfred Murrah
Federal Building in
<a href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/ok/OklahomaCity.html">Oklahoma
City</a>,
<a href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/ok/">Oklahoma</a>.</p>

<p>Timothy McVeigh and Terry Nichols were arrested as suspects and later
indicted. Nichols' brother James Nichols was questioned and arrested
on unrelated explosives charges. McVeigh's friend Michael Fortier was
indicted for consipiring with McVeigh and Nichols on various weapons
offenses.</p>

<ul>
<li>Before
	<ul>
	<li><a href="informant.html">1988: FBI informant discusses federal
		building with James Nichols</a></li>
	</ul>
<li>The bombing
	<ul>
	<li><a href="twobombs.html">One bomb or more?</a></li>
	<li><a href="tape.html">TV station documents BATF involvement?</a></li>
	<li><a href="johndoe2.html">What happened to John Doe #2?</a></li>
	</ul>
<li>The aftermath
	<ul>
	<li><a href="investigation.html">The investigation</a></li>
	<li><a href="militia.html">Some militia worried after bombing</a></li>
	<li><a
	href="/revolution/legal/police/terror95.html">Antiterrorism
		legislation gets boost</a></li>
	<li><a href="site.html">Feds block off site</a></li>
	<li>Full text of the indictments against <img src="/images/www.gif"
		alt="[WWW]"><a
		href="http://www.kwtv.com/kwtv/mcveigh.html">Timothy McVeigh
		and Terry Nichols</a> and against <img src="/images/www.gif"
		alt="[WWW]"><a
		href="http://www.kwtv.com/kwtv/fortier.html">Michael
		Fortier</a>.</li>
	</ul>
<li><a href="/revolution/by_name/N/NandO.html">NandO's</a> list of
	<img src="/images/www.gif" alt="[WWW]"><a
	href="http://www.nando.net/newsroom/oksources.html">
	OKC bombing Internet resources</a>:
	excellent list including news media, discussion groups, etc.
	on the bombing and related topics such as relief efforts and
	militias</li>
<li><img src="/images/www.gif" alt="[WWW]"><a
	href="http://www.uoknor.edu/okdaily/">University of Oklahoma student
	newspaper's</a> online site with bombing news</li>

</ul>

