<h1>Bahamas</h1>

<p>Topics:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/revolution/living/ptwatson/index.html">March 1993:
	Libertarians start Port Watson on Clove Cay, Exuma</a>
</ul>

<hr><p align=center><font size=-1 color="#990000">
