<head>
<title>Terra Libra</title>
</head>

<body>

<h1>Terra Libra</h1>

<p>Terra Libra is a libertarian multilevel marketing plan (i.e. not very
different from a pyramid scheme). Terra Librans sell "freedom technology,"
which is information about libertarianism along with some useful tools for
living free.</p>

<p>Appearances in <b>Revolution</b>:</p>
<ul>
