<head>
<title>Port Watson Experiment</title>
<!-- Place: Port Watson, Clove Cay, Exuma, Bahamas -->
<!-- Time: offer March 1993 -->
</head>

<body>

<h1>Port Watson</h1>

<p>In March 1993, a group called Port Watson Ltd. announced a new development on
an "out island" of the <a
href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/Bahamas/">Bahamas</a>. The development
would cater to libertarians and free-thinkers.</p>

<ul>
<li><a href="promo.html">Promotion Letter</a></li>
<li><a href="addendum.html">Addendum -- Cooperatives Etc.</a></li>
