<h1>Independent Institute</h1>

<p>The Independent Institute is a research and educational organization
which sponsors public policy studies and maintains the
<a href="/revolution/by_name/L/LibertyTree.html">Liberty Tree</a>
catalog of books and other items.</p>

<p>Contact:</p>
<address>
134 Ninety-Eighth Avenue<br>
Oakland, CA 94603<br>
voice: 1-800-927-8733 or 1-510-632-1366<br>
fax: 1-510-568-6040<br>
