<h1>Libertarian Elected to Delaware Town Commission</h1>

<p>In January 1996,
<a href="/revolution/by_name/L/LPUS.html">Libertarian</a> Jack Dalton
was sworn in as a Town Commissioner in
<a href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/de/Bridgeville.html">Bridgeville</a>,
<a href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/de/">Delaware</a>. Dalton is
the Sussex County representative in the Libertarian Party of Delaware.</p>

<hr>

<p>Source: March 8, 1996 advisory from the Libertarian Party.</p>

