<h1>Libertarian Appointed to Development Commission</h1>

<p>On February 8, 1996, longtime Libertarian activist Mark Seiler was
appointed to a three-year term on the
<a href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/nc/Gaston.html">Gaston County</a>
Economic Development Commission in
<a href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/nc/">North Carolina</a>.
