<head>
<title>Jeff Emery</title>
</head>
<body>

<h1>Jeff Emery</h1>

<p>Jeff Emery is the current Chair of the Libertarian Party of
New Hampshire. He has presided over a period of enormous growth
for the LPNH which has seen the election and appointment of many
Libertarians to local and state office. Emery himself won a six-year
term as Supervisor of the Checklist in Wentworth, New Hampshire in
March 1996.</p>

<p>Appearances in <b>Revolution</b>:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/revolution/politics/lpus/lpnh/mar96.html">
	March 1996 election results</a></li>
</ul>

