<html>

<head>
<title>Mathew Ignash</title>
</head>

<body>

<h1>Mathew Ignash</h1>

<p>Mathew Ignash is a Libertarian activist in Macomb County,
<a href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/mi/">Michigan</a>.
In 1995 he served as the Macomb Libertarians' Vice Chair and in 1996
ran for state representative as a Libertarian.</p>

<p>Appearances in <b>Revolution</b>:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/revolution/politics/lpus/lpmi/lmc/">Libertarians
	of Macomb County</a></li>
<li><a href="/revolution/politics/lpus/lpmi/campaign96.html">
	1996 Michigan elections</a></li>
</ul>

