<h1><cite>Liberty</cite> Magazine</h1>

<p><cite>Liberty</cite> Magazine is a relative newcomer to the libertarian
scene but quickly gained popularity for its hard-core and fun approach.
Contributors regularly include major libertarian leaders. Their new
web site contains complete text of several issues.</p>

