	href="http://www.eff.org/pub/Legislation/">legislation</a>,
	<img src="/images/www.gif" alt="[WWW]"><a
	href="http://www.eff.org/pub/Censorship/">censorship</a>,
	<img src="/images/www.gif" alt="[WWW]"><a
	href="http://www.eff.org/pub/Privacy/">privacy</a>,
	and more.</li>

<li><a href="/revolution/by_name/C/CDT.html">Center for Democracy
	and Technology</a></li>

<li><A href="/revolution/by_name/E/EPIC.html">Electronic Privacy
	Information Center</a></li>

